criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients of the Public Health System of our Country that were admitted with hip
             osteoarthritis diagnose and submitted to a total hip arthroplasty surgery in the
             Hospital de Clínicas de Porto Alegre (HCPA).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who refused to participate in this study;

          -  Patients lived in another city;

          -  Patients undergoing surgery for total hip arthroplasty due to hip fracture;

          -  Patients with cognitive disorders or diseases that adversely affect its cognitive
             function (Alzheimer's disease, senile dementia).
